organisms show the lack of consensus on this subject. Microbial risk
assessment is a relatively new area of study and has many unanswered
questions. However, further postings about infectious dose should be
directed to the original author or discussed elsewhere. Unless there is new
information pertinent to this list, this string is ended. -- Mod MDM
